&lt;p&gt;A &lt;a href="http://www.ted.com/" title="Technology Entertainment Design"&gt;TED&lt;/a&gt; talk by &lt;a href="http://www.adamsavage.com/"&gt;Adam Savage&lt;/a&gt; (of &lt;a href="http://dsc.discovery.com/fansites/mythbusters/mythbusters.html"&gt;MythBusters&lt;/a&gt;) about obsessions, starting with his own obsession over owing a replica of a &lt;a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dodo"&gt;Dodo&lt;/a&gt; skeleton to modeling a the &lt;a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Maltese_Falcon"&gt;Maltese Falcon&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Maltese_Falcon#The_falcon"&gt;Falcon&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
