&lt;p&gt;I find I am also like this with software, if I see something computer based that I find interesting I do crazy amounts of research to mimic. Recently made my site XML-RPC completely compatible with a WordPress weblog to use &lt;a href="http://iphone.wordpress.org/"&gt;WordPress iPhone&lt;/a&gt; application.&lt;/p&gt;</description><author>me@mylesbraithwaite.com (Myles Braithwaite)</author><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2009 00:00:00 -0400</pubDate><guid>http://mylesbraithwaite.com/blog/2009/jun/4/obsessions/</guid><category>Obsessions</category><category>Adam Savage</category></item></channel></rss>